1. *Bum*! (Evo!) - Boom! (Here!)
2. Danas će biti veliki *bum* na tržištu. (Today there will be a big boom in the market.)
3. Neću da te čujem, rekao sam *bum*. (I don't want to hear you, I said boom.)
4. Videla je *bum* na ulici i uplašila se. (She saw a bang on the street and got scared.)
5. Kada je iskočio iz kola, čuo se *bum*. (When he jumped out of the car, there was a bang.)
6. Ne sviđa mi se taj *bum* ton tvojih cipela. (I don't like that clunking sound of your shoes.)
7. *Bum* pitanje je da li će se to ikada desiti. (The big question is whether it will ever happen.)
8. Posle poslednjeg *buma* na berzi, ljudi su počeli da gube nadu. (After the last market crash, people started losing hope.)
9. Sela je i čekala da se čuje *bum*. (She sat and waited for the bang to be heard.)
10. Deca su se igrala, i odjednom se čuo *bum*. (The children were playing, and suddenly there was a bang.)